Subject: Re: [T2] HELP! rear end droning noise

You should jack the rear up,, and spin the wheel.
If you have a bad bearing, it will sound different side to side, so compare the
noise on the left side to the right,,

try to wiggle the tire top to bottom.. compare the amount of wiggle to the other
side of the vehicle

Jamie Rivers

